{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "12", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "12", "M": "32", "S": "27"}}, "news": [{"title": "IPO rush among developers reflects better governance, but expansion must be calibrated: Brigade Group's founder", "para": "India's real estate market is booming post-pandemic with premium homes gaining traction. However, mid-income and mass housing remain key. Brigade Group's M.R. Jaishankar highlights the need for government support in affordable housing and developer caution on expansion. The sector's long-term outlook is positive, driven by economic growth and rising incomes.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/ipo-rush-among-developers-reflects-better-governance-but-expansion-must-be-calibrated-brigade-groups-founder/129457457?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-101636/129457457.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Centre gives nod for \u20b91,250 crore IT park in Puducherry", "para": "Puducherry is set to establish a dedicated IT Special Economic Zone (SEZ) with Union government approval, costing Rs1,250 crore. This 'Work-Live-Play' mini-city on 21.3 acres aims to retain local talent by creating 30,000 jobs and boosting service exports, transforming the region into a tech hub.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/centre-approves-1250-crore-it-park-to-transform-puducherry-into-tech-hub/129488728?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-253777/129488728.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Mumbai: MHADA \u2018duped of\u2019 \u20b9121 crore rent in 25 years", "para": "Maharashtra Housing and Area Development Authority (MHADA) has been defrauded of over Rs 121 crore. Ten developers allegedly failed to pay rent for transit tenements for 25 years